Package: libinsight
Type: Package
Title: Library Statistics Analysis and Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-04-13
Author: Sahl Mohammed
Maintainer: Sahl Mohammed <sahlmohammedwork@gmail.com>
Description: Library insight - functions for working with statistics of academic
    libraries. It includes functions to compute library circulation summaries,
    identify most circulated items, create patron profile, check collection aging
    and generate heatmap and trend plot visualizations. Also, it contains S3
    class 'libdata' which is a library dataset type. Designed to be useful for
    librarians, information scientists and LIS researchers who work with R.
